# TableGrid Implementation Report — Phase 13.3

## Files Modified

| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| `src/JLek.POS.Web/Components/Cashier/TableGrid/TableGrid.razor` | Complete rewrite with keyboard navigation, aria labels, status colors, loading/error/empty states, double-click support, refresh parameter |

## Components Implemented

### TableGrid
| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| Loading state | 8 skeleton cards with pulse animation, `aria-label="Loading tables"` |
| Error state | Error message + [Retry] button, `role="alert"` |
| Empty state | "No tables available" message |
| Data state | Grid of TableCard items with status colors |
| Keyboard navigation | Arrow keys move focus, Enter selects, F5 refreshes |
| ARIA | `role="grid"`, `role="gridcell"`, `aria-selected`, `aria-label` per card |
| Double-click | `OnDoubleClick` EventCallback for open table shortcut |
| Refresh | `RefreshVersion` parameter triggers reload |
| Status colors | Available=#22c55e(green), Occupied=#f97316(orange), Reserved=#3b82f6(blue), Cleaning=#9ca3af(gray) |

### TableCard (inline in TableGrid)
| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| Display | Table name, status text, color indicator bar |
| Selection | Selected state with checkmark indicator |
| Touch target | min 120×80px card |
| Colors | Border + indicator match status color |

